Package: PiecewiseChangepoint
Type: Package
Title: Piecewise Exponential Models with Unknown Change-points
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-09-01
Authors@R: person("Philip", "Cooney", email = "phcooney@tcd.ie",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An implementation of the piecewise exponential models with unknown change-points using a Bayesian framework. Also provides methods to compare against other commonly used parametric survival models.
